data.description: Final reduction! Move in ready Citrus Springs home, like new, all the extras have already been done for you.  No carpet, all laminate flooring except for the baths.  You will love this split floor plan with a barn door separating the 2 oversized bedrooms from the great room area for added privacy.  This has a beautiful open floor plan which includes a large dining room area and great room.  All overlooked by this gorgeous kitchen with an island that can be used as a breakfast bar, dark wood cabinets, stainless steel appliances and large pantry.  A sliding glass door from the great room takes you out to the concrete pad perfect for your grill and to enjoy the lovely back yard.  Ceramic tiled baths.  Inside laundry with shelving and the washer and dryer that is staying.  From here step out into the garage with plenty of storage space where you will see another added feature, the epoxy floor, beautiful!!!  Lots of big furniture can fit into the master bedroom with two closets, one a walk in. The tiled master bath contains a tiled walk in shower and extra large vanity with mirror. Fans in all rooms. All the windows in this home make it light and bright!!  So much usable space.  Vacant lots behind, next door and across the street for added privacy.  No need to look elsewhere when everything has been done so make your appointment today. If buyer uses our preferred lender, Jay Bruno from Supreme Lending, a $2,000 credit will be given towards closing costs as well as a free appraisal.
